title: Guess What Day It Is?!? Guess What Day It Is?!?

description:
WED 6/29 - It's the day The Breakfast Club has dreaded all month long...CHARLAMAGNE'S BIRTHDAY! The loveable a-hole himself makes sure we all know that this Hump Day is HIS! We also get a visit from Jim Jones, who doesn't sound like he's ready to hand out beef-squashing gifts to too many people.
